613
00:39:19,524 --> 00:39:22,825
You cleaned all of your
clothes out of the house.

614
00:39:22,928 --> 00:39:24,977
Go home, Meredith. Just go home.

615
00:39:25,079 --> 00:39:27,530
How long are you
planning on hiding out here?

616
00:39:27,632 --> 00:39:30,183
That's what you're
doing. You're hiding.

617
00:39:30,285 --> 00:39:35,337
You made a mistake, she's
dead. You can't hide from that.

618
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:38,557
I'm not hiding, I'm done.

619
00:39:38,659 --> 00:39:40,677
I'm done operating.

620
00:39:40,779 --> 00:39:42,779
Oh, OK, so you're just quitting?

621
00:39:42,881 --> 00:39:46,249
You should understand,
you wrote the book on quitting,

622
00:39:46,351 --> 00:39:49,668
running, hiding... You've
written a lot of books, Meredith.

623
00:39:49,770 --> 00:39:53,222
That may be true,
but I'm here now.

624
00:39:54,726 --> 00:39:57,710
You're here now?

625
00:39:59,181 --> 00:40:02,865
- You wanted me out
since I moved in.
- That is not true.

626
00:40:02,968 --> 00:40:06,152
You are incapable of anything
that resembles commitment.

627
00:40:06,254 --> 00:40:09,688
You lied to me. You
said you were healthier,

628
00:40:09,790 --> 00:40:11,457
you were healed.

629
00:40:11,559 --> 00:40:14,159
There's no fixing
you. You're a lemon.

630
00:40:14,261 --> 00:40:16,195
Derek Shepherd, you are drunk.

631
00:40:17,716 --> 00:40:20,650
And you're angry. And
I've been there, so I get it.

632
00:40:20,752 --> 00:40:23,369
- That doesn't
give you the right...
- Go home.

633
00:40:23,471 --> 00:40:25,549
- You don't get to...
- This is what you want,

634
00:40:25,573 --> 00:40:27,293
I'm giving you an out. Go!

635
00:40:27,358 --> 00:40:30,994
- I'm not going anywhere.
- I said leave! Meredith, leave!

636
00:40:37,735 --> 00:40:40,819
I know there's a ring.

637
00:40:42,357 --> 00:40:44,873
- What?
- The chief told me.

638
00:40:44,976 --> 00:40:46,859
I know there's a ring.

639
00:40:48,814 --> 00:40:52,248
<i>♪ Black crows
circling up above ♪</i>

640
00:40:52,350 --> 00:40:54,049
You want the ring?

641
00:40:56,203 --> 00:40:59,072
<i>♪ I never thought
