645
00:41:13,487 --> 00:41:17,540
That the best you've got? I'm
not bailing. We're in this together.

646
00:41:18,577 --> 00:41:20,410
Go home, Meredith.

647
00:41:20,512 --> 00:41:23,379
<i>And the only way to
get rid of a shadow...</i>

